  m_Name: GSWGA_Course_2_Final_Assessment_Q2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: 'A company develops an AI-powered hiring platform and the tool is trained
    on diverse demographic data to minimize bias. The platform is also regularly
    tested to promote equitable treatment across all candidates.

    Which ethical
    pillar does this scenario best demonstrate?'
  answers:
  - Accountability
  - Transparency
  - Fairness
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 02000000
  correctMessage: Fairness promotes AI tools that are inclusive, minimize bias, and
    provide equitable outcomes for all individuals.
  incorrectMessage: Not quite. Consider which pillar focuses on reducing bias and
    equitable treatment in AI applications.
